instalación boost
sudo apt update
sudo apt install libboost-all-dev

instalación nlohmann/json
sudo apt install nlohmann-json3-dev

instalacion crow
mkdir external (en la raiz del proyecto)
cd external
wget https://github.com/CrowCpp/Crow/releases/download/v1.0/crow_all.h

Luego:
ctrl + shift + p en VSCode -> C/Cpp: Editar configuraciones de usuario (JSON)
c/c++ edit configurations JSON

{
  "configurations": [
    {
      "name": "Linux",
      "includePath": [
        "${workspaceFolder}/**",
        "${workspaceFolder}/external"
      ],
      "compilerPath": "/usr/bin/g++",
      "cStandard": "c17",
      "cppStandard": "c++17",
      "intelliSenseMode": "linux-gcc-x64"
    }
  ],
  "version": 4
}

Ejecución:
mkdir build
cd build
cmake ..
make
./build/clase1

curl "http://localhost:8080/analizar?file=testdata/entrada.txt"